 provide your analysis on how you count \"often\"?\r\n\r\ncause its not with coreutils 8.31, `ls`:\r\n```\r\n$> touch foo Foo bar Bar\r\n$> \\ls\r\nbar  Bar  foo  Foo\r\n```\r\n\r\nnor `sort`:\r\n```\r\n$> \\ls | \\sort\r\nbar\r\nBar\r\nfoo\r\nFoo\r\n```\r\n\r\n> `\\` is used here to bypass aliases.\r\n\r\n## \"ensuring files like Makefile and Cargo.toml are placed together\"\r\n\r\ndid you know that `make` also reads `makefile`?\r\n\r\nso please follow `make`s lead and also read `cargo.toml`.", "closed_by": {"login": "hlb-schmidt", "id": 11519445, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjExNTE5NDQ1", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/11519445?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/hlb-schmidt", "html_url": "https://github.com/hlb-schmidt", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/hlb-schmidt/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/hlb-schmidt/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/hlb-schmidt/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/hlb-schmidt/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/hlb-schmidt/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/hlb-schmidt/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/hlb-schmidt/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/hlb-schmidt/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/hlb-schmidt/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/65304/reactions", "total_count": 1, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 1, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/65304/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": null, "state_reason": "completed"}